    "description": "In My Shadow将带你走进一个悲伤的梦境,在那里用自己独特的想象力与影子玩耍,解决那些困难的平台谜题.<br>游戏讲述了一个年轻女人贝拉的故事,多年前她与家人决裂,现在发现自己正在试着回复父亲的消息.童年的记忆以影子的形式出现在家里的墙上,你需要借助这些影子来解决独特的谜题,帮助贝拉试着放下过去.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>哪里有影子,哪里就有路</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/f69482e19397bf8f01d1cf2c6b20ed17.poster.avif?t=1637842084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/f69482e19397bf8f01d1cf2c6b20ed17.webm?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/f69482e19397bf8f01d1cf2c6b20ed17.mp4?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏的核心玩法——阴影.你可以随心所欲地借助各种影子,同样的谜题有着多样的解法.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>影子没有边界</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/792defdc831fab122d1dda5f76a64604.poster.avif?t=1637842084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/792defdc831fab122d1dda5f76a64604.webm?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/792defdc831fab122d1dda5f76a64604.mp4?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏将不断用多维度的机制挑战你,迫使你找到使用影子的新方法.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/5c5616cbc154e5b9f36eca0c13f49dec.poster.avif?t=1637842084\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/5c5616cbc154e5b9f36eca0c13f49dec.webm?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406200/extras/5c5616cbc154e5b9f36eca0c13f49dec.mp4?t=1637842084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>令人耳目一新的新奇谜题,从未设想的方式利用阴影和形状.<br></li><li>四个房间的墙壁上分布了50多个关卡,每个关卡都有一套独特的机制.<br></li><li>一个关于贝拉心理创伤,童年记忆的动人故事.<br></li><li>游戏的音乐旋律在游戏流程中无缝衔接,烘托加强故事情感.<br></li><li>色彩鲜明的贝拉之家,展现出家人各异的个性.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
